				<h2>Answer</h2>
				<h3>Score ::4</h3>
				<p><p>I would say yes, they are on topic. It has been my intention that the scope of this site would involve all aspects of Apple products, and I don't see any reason why fink, ports, or homebrew should be excepted.</p>

<p>Again, like the <a href="https://apple.meta.stackexchange.com/questions/513/question-about-a-windows-driver-here-or-super-user">question about a Windows driver</a>, this is not to say that there aren't other sites on the network where the question may also be asked, or where they may even receive a better answer. But those aren't reason enough, in my opinion, to remove them from the scope of this site.</p>
</p><br>
